  "title": "Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<h3>About Us</h3><p>The Prosthetic Company is a people-focused social enterprise dedicated to empowering lives through innovation, inclusivity, and care. We’re looking for a creative and driven <strong>Marketing Executive</strong> to join our team and help us amplify our impact.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Develop and execute marketing campaigns across digital and offline platforms.</li><li>Create engaging content (videos, graphics, social posts) to strengthen brand presence.</li><li>Manage social media channels and track performance metrics.</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams to support events, outreach, and community engagement.</li><li>Contribute fresh ideas to enhance brand storytelling and audience engagement.</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>Proficiency in <strong>CapCut</strong> (video editing) and <strong>Canva</strong> (graphic design).</li><li>Strong communication and writing skills.</li><li>Creative mindset with attention to detail.</li><li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</li><li>Prior experience in marketing, communications, or related fields preferred.</li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li>Competitive salary based on experience (SGD 2,800 – 3,500).</li><li>Opportunity to make a meaningful impact in a social enterprise.</li><li>Supportive and inclusive work environment.</li><li>Professional growth and creative freedom.</li></ul>",
